Package com.siperian.sif.message.mrm Description

MRM message API.

Each MRM service has a pair of messages: request and response. Typical usage is to instantiate and populate a request (subclass of SiperianRequest), then call the SiperianClient.process() method, and cast the response (subclass of SiperianResponse), to the corresponding response class. For example:

GetRequest get = new GetRequest();
// ... set request parameters
GetResponse response = (GetResponse) client.process(get);
